{"tid":795249,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[學術討論] 點解我要生存落去？","createTime":"2018-08-27T00:39:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-30T00:49:05.000Z","uid":125976,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"87049e4721873fc487546a9d3611df19c0a78a33","tid":795249,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T00:39:32.000Z","msg":"According to Maslow's Hierarchy of Needs<br />\n人類嘅最終追求係「實踐自我」。<br />\n<br />\n又有人話，人類生存就係「追求快樂，逃避痛苦」。<br />\n<br />\n但小弟出身一般，仲要出生喺香港依個極端貧富懸殊嘅地區。一出世就好似已經注定咗要幫地產霸權打一世牛工，做大公司、大家族腳下嘅「齒輪」，完全冇可能「實踐自我」。<br />\n<br />\n至於「追求快樂」，既然出身一般，咁就冇足夠資源「追求快樂」 (eg. 學習、外遊、買奢侈品)。<br />\n<br />\n咁嘅奴隸人生，日復日、年復年，唔係寧願冇生存過好過？<br />\n<br />\n小弟唔係想鼓勵人輕生，只係大家係咪要反思一吓繼續做「港豬」嘅意義？"},{"pid":"a9bf8cc2858d7cd59f38d39eddadf6f2bb48deaa","tid":795249,"uid":43046,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T00:44:39.000Z","msg":"According to Maslow's Hierarchy of Needs<br />\n<br />\n呢句睇到好尷尬<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10b095b4b4fda9650284905115aff3518aad2155","tid":795249,"uid":125976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a9bf8cc2858d7cd59f38d39eddadf6f2bb48deaa","tid":795249,"uid":43046,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T00:44:39.000Z","msg":"According to Maslow's Hierarchy of Needs<br />\n<br />\n呢句睇到好尷尬<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T00:49:35.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，家貧，文化差，用詞差，請見諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c72c52bc8710ca1948264e8d314d1a47631e1564","tid":795249,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T01:17:04.000Z","msg":"點樣奴隸法先 你依家滿足到第幾層嘅 needs 呀"},{"pid":"77e9298008953133a850454b862199eb5e368288","tid":795249,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score